[section 2 Druids]

You are proficient with weapons up to d6 and armor up to type 4. While you
are wielding a metal weapon or wearing metal armor, you cannot cast spells.

Your spellcasting ability is Perception. You have a pool of 8 mana points.

When you cast a spell in a place of natural beauty, it costs one fewer mana
points, to a minimum of one mana.

