[section 2 Rogues]

You are proficient with weapons up to d8 and armor up to type 4.

A rogue's base Evd score is equal to their Spd plus their Dex, minus
their Size.

The first time each turn that you make a surprise attack or attack a creature
that is being flanked, you have a +2 to hit and roll an additional d4/4
for damage.

