[section 2 Wizards]

You are proficient with weapons up to d6 and armor up to type 2.

Your spellcasting ability is Inte. You have a pool of 16 mana points.

You can cast the following spells without a spellstone:

[text ib Arcane Armor.] You gain one shield point that lasts until the start of
your next turn.

[text ib Arcane Dart.] Make a 1-damage magic attack with range 10.

